                <p>Hi my name is Alfredo, and I am aspiring to become a software engineer</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4">
            <div class="box">
                <button class="img-btn" data-id="3">
                    <img src="./images/Daniil.png" class="img-fluid mb-3 w-50"  alt="Team Member 3">
                </button>
                <p>Hello I am Daniil, I am mainly responsible for front end programming and UI design</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4">
            <div class="box">
